                    "body": "I don't think that this is needed anymore.\n\nYou can set different messages per instance which already worked before.\nOr you can use translation and attach it to the instance, which will then translate the messages.\n\nThe result is the same as before because you will always use the same translation, but have still the ability to change the content manually.\n",
